<h2>jQuery Plugin : Form</h2>
<div class="desc">
	form 전송의 비동기 처리를 지원하는 Plugin<br><br>
	
	참조 : <a href="http://malsup.com/jquery/form/" target="_blank">jQuery Form Plugin</a>
</div>
<article>
	<h3>Html</h3>
	<div class="code">
		<pre class="brush: xml;">
			&lt;script src="./scripts/jquery/plugin/jquery.form.min.js">&lt;/script>
			
			&lt;form id="myForm" action="comment.php" method="post"> 
			    Name: &lt;input type="text" name="name" /> 
			    Comment: &lt;textarea name="comment">&lt;/textarea> 
			    &lt;input type="submit" value="Submit Comment" /> 
			&lt;/form>
		</pre>
	</div>
	<h3>Js</h3>
	<div class="code">
		<pre class="brush: js;">
	        (function( $, window, document){
				$(function(){
					//======================== page initialize ===================
					
					var options =  {
							beforeSubmit 	: function () {},		// beforeHandler : use validate, loading...
							success 		: function () {}		// successHandler
						};
					
					$('#myForm').ajaxForm(options);
		            
					//============================================================
				});
			})( jQuery, window, document );
		</pre>
	</div>
</article>


